<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1334884-the-crude-nature-of-the-mindsets">The crude nature of the mindsets portrayed..I’m rural Irish through and through but it is hard for me to believe that swathes of people around and about think in such reductive and crude narrow deminsional ways. I ‘ve rarely met men who are so blunted and crude and the portrayal of his women lack nuance and dimension and appear to function as little other than male support ...it grates to read but should I read on?</a>
</div>
