<span id="freeTextContainer5536570508224991837">This is an amazing story told by many voices during an economical collapse in a small Irish town. It&apos;s incredible that a novel can be presented from multiple points-of-view and yet remain cohesive. This story will touch on all of your emotions and leave you satisfied when it is all over. I highly recommend this read! </span>
  <span id="freeText5536570508224991837" style="display:none">This is an amazing story told by many voices during an economical collapse in a small Irish town. It's incredible that a novel can be presented from multiple points-of-view and yet remain cohesive. This story will touch on all of your emotions and leave you satisfied when it is all over. I highly recommend this read! </span>
