<span id="freeTextContainer13918130485214587690"> I thought that in such a short book the author managed to convey a wide panorama of the impact of the economic crash in Ireland. There were so many voices in this book; Ryan was masterful.<br/><br/>Read a second time and it was better the second time.</span>

